authorName.value: Climate Change Agriculture and Food Security

dsDescriptionValue.value:
This study contains files produced for and generated by the CCAFS Village Baseline Study which was run in core sites in East
& West Africa and South Asia.  The study includes several activities involving members of the local communities; photos and maps from these activities are available in this archive.  Before downloading any of the files, particularly the mitigation data file, please download and read the ReadMe file and the Data Quality Summary in the 00 CCAFS ReadMe section of this archive.  Details of the activities for the study can be found in the Manuals section.
